RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT B.ENTITY, B.ENTITY_NAME, B.ENTITY_TYPE FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER_ENTITY_DETAILS B WHERE CUSTOMER_NO = ?
SELECT CUSTOMER_NO, SHORT_NAME, CUSTOMER_NAME1 FROM OLTMS_CUSTOMER WHERE RECORD_STAT = 'O' AND AUTH_STAT = 'A'

SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO,B.DIARY_EVENT_SEQ_NO,B.DIARY_EVENT_SUB_SEQ_NO, A.TREASURY_SOURCE, A.DEPARTMENT_CODE FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A,OLTBS_CONTRACT_DIARY_STATUS B WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO=B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND sypks_utils.get_branch(A.CONTRACT_REF_NO)=?

RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_SUMMARY_WHERECLAUSE: sypks_utils.get_branch(CONTRACT_REF_NO) = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH and exists (Select 1 From OLVW_USER_ACCESS_PRODUCTS Where PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND USER_ID = global.user_id)
RAD_SUMMARY.RAD_MULTIBRN_WHERECLAUSE: sypks_utils.get_branch(CONTRACT_REF_NO) IN (SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVW_USER_BRANCHES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID INTERSECT SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMTB_USER_ROLE WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID UNION SELECT BRANCH_CODE FROM SMVWS_USER_CENTRAL_ROLES WHERE USER_ID = GLOBAL.USER_ID) and exists (Select 1 From OLVW_USER_ACCESS_PRODUCTS Where PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(CONTRACT_REF_NO) AND USER_ID = global.user_id)

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.EVENT, A.EVENT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_DIARY_EVENT_DEFN A, LFTMS_PRODUCT_DIARY_EVENT B WHERE B.PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(?) AND A.EVENT = B.EVENT_CODE AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT WHERE PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(?) AND MODULE = A.MODULE)

SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO,B.DIARY_EVENT_SEQ_NO,B.DIARY_EVENT_SUB_SEQ_NO FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A,OLTBS_CONTRACT_DIARY_STATUS B WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO=B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND sypks_utils.get_branch(A.CONTRACT_REF_NO)=GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH
